00:00:25,619 --> 00:00:27,119
must be with your grandfather.

14
00:00:27,121 --> 00:00:28,954
Waverider crew, we are now the proud owners

15
00:00:28,956 --> 00:00:31,123
of the last fragment
of the Spear of Destiny.

16
00:00:31,125 --> 00:00:33,459
Back in 1942, you have a
destiny waiting for you.

17
00:00:33,461 --> 00:00:35,177
Ask Ray what happens
to your village, ask him

18
00:00:35,179 --> 00:00:37,346
what happens to your daughter
and your granddaughter,

19
00:00:37,348 --> 00:00:40,766
and tell me you'll choose
history over your own family.

20
00:00:42,803 --> 00:00:43,802
Watch out, lads!

21
00:00:43,804 --> 00:00:45,304
- _
