Please don't tell me you
used the Spear of Destiny

36
00:01:34,522 --> 00:01:35,854
as a back scratcher.

37
00:01:35,856 --> 00:01:38,323
Who said anything about my back?

38
00:01:38,325 --> 00:01:40,359
Well, as Mr. Rory has demonstrated,

39
00:01:40,361 --> 00:01:41,610
in the wrong hands,

40
