Probably not.

95
00:04:41,208 --> 00:04:42,791
Hold on a sec.

96
00:04:42,793 --> 00:04:44,927
That looks like something
you might hide something in.

97
00:04:48,432 --> 00:04:50,299
Yes, it does.

98
00:04:50,301 --> 00:04:52,851
Jax and I may have found the
other pieces of the spear.

99
00:04:52,853 --> 00:04:54,636
Standby.

100
