00:10:40,067 --> 00:10:43,568
Well, looks like we're going back to war.

225
00:10:49,286 --> 00:10:51,620
Temper, temper.

226
00:10:51,622 --> 00:10:53,322
Don't test me, Damien!

227
00:10:53,324 --> 00:10:54,990
Shouldn't it be the other way around?

228
00:10:54,992 --> 00:10:58,243
You sent me and Malcolm off
to find the Kalabros Manuscript

229
00:10:58,245 --> 00:10:59,712
while the Legends managed to abscond

