00:11:01,499 --> 00:11:03,248
I should have that zombie Speedster

232
00:11:03,250 --> 00:11:06,168
you're so afraid of eat your brain.

233
00:11:06,170 --> 00:11:07,836
No.

234
00:11:07,838 --> 00:11:11,390
No, this is actually
a positive development.

235
00:11:11,392 --> 00:11:13,258
Or maybe he already has.

236
00:11:13,260 --> 00:11:15,978
With the entire spear in
the Legends' possession,

237
00:11:15,980 --> 00:11:18,347
