242
00:11:29,026 --> 00:11:31,076
- No.
- Excuse me?

243
00:11:31,078 --> 00:11:32,694
Not just us.

244
00:11:32,696 --> 00:11:34,913
I'm not sure if you're
keeping score, Eobard,

