The Battle of the Somme was
one of the bloodiest conflicts

249
00:11:51,382 --> 00:11:52,681
in human history.

250
00:11:52,683 --> 00:11:54,216
Sounds terrible. I'm in.

251
00:11:54,218 --> 00:11:55,801
We're all in.

