257
00:12:05,446 --> 00:12:08,063
Perfect. Amaya, take the Backstreet Boys,

258
00:12:08,065 --> 00:12:10,232
intercept Tolkien, find out what he knows,

259
00:12:10,234 --> 00:12:11,366
send him on his way.

260
00:12:11,368 --> 00:12:12,734
So what'd you want us to do?

